projects.name: Food Delevering Web App
projects.description: Created a secure food delevering app with Express and MongoDB backend, implementing authentication for user data protection and also used Razorpay for payment gateway integration. Builds its frontend in React- Js and used Redux from state management.

projects.name: Chat Bot
projects.description: Developed a chatbot application using React.js and Material UI, integrating Google Authentication and Firebase for secure user login and real-time data storage. The chatbot provides responsive, intuitive user interactions and leverages Firebases cloud functions for backend logic, ensuring seamless, reliable performance and a polished user interface.

projects.name: Library Store
projects.description: Developed a library store application using React.js for dynamic UI rendering and Axios for seamless API integration. Enabled efficient book search ,user management, and real-time updates.

experiences.description: Developed a comprehensive admin dashboard using Spring Framework and SpringBoot, enabling efficient user management, real-time data analytics, and system monitoring. Implemented secure authentication and authorization mechanisms, optimized database interactions with JPA/Hibernate, and integrated RESTful APIs for seamless data communication. Enhanced user experience with a responsive and intuitive UI using Thymeleaf and Bootstrap.
